'''花柱'''（{{lang-en|style}}），是[[花|花]]中[[雌蕊|雌蕊]]的一部分，連接[[柱頭|柱頭]]與[[子房|子房]]。花柱通常為管狀，並可為空心或實心。[[花粉管|花粉管]]在柱頭萌發後生長經過花柱內部而到達[[胚珠|胚珠]]，在一些例子中花柱也負責執行[[孢子體|孢子體]][[自交不親和性|自交不親和性]]，可阻止花粉管完全生長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2594090|title=Style self-incompatibility gene products of Nicotiana alata are ribonucleases.|publisher=[[Nature|Nature]]|author=McClure BA et al|date=1989-12-21|accessdate=2015-01-22|archive-date=2015-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122045158/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/2594090|dead-url=no}}</ref>。花柱可能具有引導花粉管抵達胚珠的作用，具體方法可能是透過花粉管與花柱通道的黏著<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1676050/|title=Exogenous Free Ubiquitin Enhances Lily Pollen Tube Adhesion to an in Vitro Stylar Matrix and May Facilitate Endocytosis of SCA|publisher=Plant Physiology|author=Sun Tae Kim, Elizabeth M. Lord|date=2006-12}}</ref>。

==花柱长度变异现象==
某些植物同一物种的花柱长度存在变异。例如[[小花风毛菊|小花风毛菊]]的花柱及其[[柱头|柱头]]分叉长度会随着海拔的升高显著增长<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yi-Feng |first1=Wang |last2=Hong-Yan |first2=G. a. O. |last3=Hai-Yan |first3=S. H. I. |last4=Jian-Hong |first4=Wang |last5=Guo-Zhen |first5=D. U. |title=ADAPTIVE SIGNIFICANCE OF SAUSSUREA PARVIFLORA’S SEXUAL ORGANS, QINGHAI-TIBETAN PLATEAU, CHINA |journal=Chinese Journal of Plant Ecology |date=2008-03-30 |volume=32 |issue=2 |pages=379 |doi=10.3773/j.issn.1005-264x.2008.02.015}}</ref>；[[欧洲千里光|欧洲千里光]]的花柱长度可分为长柱型和短柱型<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Love |first1=John |last2=Graham |first2=Sean W. |last3=Irwin |first3=Judith A. |last4=Ashton |first4=Paul A. |last5=Bretagnolle |first5=Francois |last6=Abbott |first6=Richard J. |title=Self-pollination, style length development and seed set in self-compatible Asteraceae: evidence from Senecio vulgaris L. |journal=Plant Ecology & Diversity |date=2016-07-03 |volume=9 |issue=4 |pages=371–379 |doi=10.1080/17550874.2016.1244576}}</ref>。

花柱长度的变异可能与[[花|花]]大小、[[花粉|花粉]]体积、[[花粉管|花粉管]]生长速率、花粉败育比率等有关，更长的花柱可能更有利于传粉和繁殖<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xiaoyue |first1=Wang |last2=Xinxin |first2=Zhu |last3=Juan |first3=Yang |last4=Yunjing |first4=Liu |last5=Xiaoxin |first5=Tang |title=Variation in style length and the effect on reproductive success in Chinese plums (Armeniaca mume) |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019 |volume=27 |issue=2 |pages=159–167 |doi=10.17520/biods.2018317}}</ref>。

